metadata.name: ART TO THE RESCUE
metadata.description:
During the 24 years of my existence, art has been a savior. From being the only friend at school to an everyday escape art has played many roles in my life. This artwork is representation of art rescuing a lifeless thing from boredom and abandonment, i am not good at narrating story so i decided to paint it.

Digital painting
4385px * 5422px
